\par }\pard\plain \s16\qj\nowidctlpar\widctlpar\adjustright \lang2057 {\rdblquote I cannot say with <-/certanity> who injured <name/> but from (the) circumstances, I can say that it is you because you went for her and she was okay. <#/>\'94
