e presence of the said drugs inside the said room and that is why he sought to keep the police out. <#/>He was alone inside the room. <#/>We are satisfied that he was found in possession of the said cannabis sativa (<ea/>bhang) within the meaning of the D
a
ngerous Drugs Act: <name/> -V- The Republic (1980) KLAR 139. <#/>Since he was alone in the locked room where the said drugs were found, we believe that he had the physical control over such drugs and was in a position to deal with the him as an owner coul
